Feature:Update A New Person

  Scenario Outline: Update an existing person in the application

    When I update the details of a person with name <firstname> and <lastname>
    When The details are updated with <firstnameupdated>
    Then The new data for <firstnameupdated>  is displayed

    Examples:
      | firstname | lastname | firstnameupdated |
      | Mark      | Antony   | Marc             |
